hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有四维的度规
$$ds^2=-dt^2+dx^2+R^2\bigl(d\theta^2+\sin^2\theta\,d\phi^2\bigr)\,. $$  
唯一非零的克里斯托费尔符号来自 $S^2$ 部分：
$$\Gamma^\theta_{\phi\phi}=-\tfrac12\,g^{\theta\theta}\,\partial_\theta g_{\phi\phi}
=-\frac{1}{2R^2}(2R^2\sin\theta\cos\theta)=-\sin\theta\cos\theta\,,$$  
$$\Gamma^\phi_{\theta\phi}=\Gamma^\phi_{\phi\theta}
=\tfrac12\,g^{\phi\phi}\,\partial_\theta g_{\phi\phi}
=\frac{1}{2R^2\sin^2\theta}(2R^2\sin\theta\cos\theta)=\cot\theta\,. $$  
所有其他的 $\Gamma^\lambda_{\mu\nu}$ 均为零。

现在计算
$$R_{\theta\theta}
=\partial_\rho\Gamma^\rho_{\theta\theta}-\partial_\theta\Gamma^\rho_{\rho\theta}
+\Gamma^\rho_{\rho\sigma}\Gamma^\sigma_{\theta\theta}
-\Gamma^\rho_{\theta\sigma}\Gamma^\sigma_{\theta\rho}\,. $$  
逐项分析：
1. $\partial_\rho\Gamma^\rho_{\theta\theta}=0$ 因为 $\Gamma^\rho_{\theta\theta}=0$。
2. $-\partial_\theta\Gamma^\rho_{\rho\theta}
=-\partial_\theta(\Gamma^\phi_{\phi\theta})
=-\partial_\theta(\cot\theta)=+\csc^2\theta\,. $
3. $\Gamma^\rho_{\rho\sigma}\Gamma^\sigma_{\theta\theta}=0$ 因为 $\Gamma^\sigma_{\theta\theta}=0$。
4. $-\Gamma^\rho_{\theta\sigma}\Gamma^\sigma_{\theta\rho}
=-\Gamma^\phi_{\theta\phi}\Gamma^\phi_{\theta\phi}
=-(\cot\theta)^2\,. $

因此
$$R_{\theta\theta}
=\csc^2\theta-(\cot\theta)^2
=\frac{1-\cos^2\theta}{\sin^2\theta}=1\,. $$
